Rep. Livingston was accused of hypocrisy when he disclosed 
extramarital affairs of his own. Convinced that his personal 
history would have interfered with his ability to lead, Rep. 
Livingston shocked his colleagues by stepping aside. ... 
</P>
<P>
	Life goes on. In time, the trauma of the impeachment debate will  
fade, and Louisiana's delegation will slowly rebuild its clout in 
Washington. If New Orleans area residents are lucky, our future 
representatives in Congress will display the same professionalism, 
diligence and political integrity that Mr. Livingston possesses. 

