40. Actress Camryn Manheim (``The Practice'') is 38. Actress Andrea 
Parker (``The Pretender'') is 30. Actor Freddie Prinze Jr. (``She's 
All That'') is 23. Actor James Van Der Beek (``Dawson's Creek'') is 
22. 
</P>
